115
00:10:52,836 --> 00:10:56,178
Our side yard along Harvard Street has been slightly decreased.

116
00:10:57,458 --> 00:11:04,642
Our max height has been reduced, therefore shrinking our variance there, and our lot coverage has also been reduced.

117
00:11:06,063 --> 00:11:19,426
Now, as a result of the modifications, we will be seeking three variances, one of which is a modification, two of which will be quote-unquote new variances.

118
00:11:19,506 --> 00:11:31,288
