941
01:48:04,038 --> 01:48:14,806
as we continue to develop the design, the pedestrian, the road will be designed in such a way to ensure pedestrian safety.

942
01:48:16,227 --> 01:48:22,451
The other two things that are related to this topic is parking has come up as a question.

943
01:48:23,491 --> 01:48:31,717
So the current parking on site is 0.28 parking spaces per unit.

944
01:48:32,302 --> 01:48:42,086
